IF CLAUSE/ CONDITIONAL SENTENCES

TYPE 1 : Future Possible
IF S + V_1 + O, S + Will V_1 + O (+)
IF S + V_1 + O, Imperative! 

TYPE 2 : Present Unreal
IF S + V_2  + O, S + Would V_1+ O (+)
IF S + Did not V_1 + O, S + Would not V_1 + O (-)

TYPE 3 : Past Unreal
IF S + Had V_3  + O, S + Would Have V_3+ O (+)
IF S + Had not V_3 + O, S + Would not have V_3 + O (-)

